H0.text: What was the pre-independence name of Malawi. British Central Africa

H1.text: What was the pre-independence name of Malawi. Shire Highlands

H2.text: What was the pre-independence name of Malawi. Lake Nyasa Districts

H3.text: What was the pre-independence name of Malawi. NYASALAND

A4.text: Nyasaland was a British protectorate established in 1907 when the former British Central Africa Protectorate changed its name.

A5.text: Nyasaland became independent from Britain on 6 July 1964 and was renamed Malawi.
